        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3Etranscript%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%3Ch1%3ETranscript%3C%2Fh1%3E%0ATranscript%20of%20an%20online%20discussion%20carried%20by%20America%20Online%20and%0Aled%20from%20the%20National%20Demonstration%20Laboratory%20at%20the%20Library%20of%0ACongress%20by%20James%20Billington%2C%20Librarian%20of%20Congress%2C%20and%20Rudolf%0APikhoia%2C%20Russian%20Archivist.%20%20The%20event%20took%20place%20June%2018%2C%201992.%0A%0A%3Cdl%3E%0A%3Cdt%3EAFL%20Bobloo%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ESovarc%2C%20I'm%20curious%20as%20to%20how%20the%20Russian%20people%0Afeel%20about%20this%20exhibit%3F%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EWe%20have%20to%20say%20that%20not%20only%20Americans%20have%20not%20seen%0Athese%20documents%2C%20but%20Russians%20have%20never%20seen%20these.%20%20We%20have%0Abeen%20preparing%20a%20series%20of%20useful%20exhibits%20for%20high%20school%20and%0Acollege%20students.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EAFL%20Bobloo%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ESo%20we%20are%20all%20seeing%20these%20things%20for%20the%20first%0Atime.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ETipToe%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EI'm%20asking%20this%20on%20behalf%20of%20Mick%20Anderson%20(7th%0Agrade)%3A%20Is%20this%20a%202-way%20exchange%20of%20information%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ETipToe%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EAre%20we%20making%20American%20documents%20available%20to%0ARussian%20people%20through%20schools%20or%20anything%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EAFC%20SteveB%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3E%5BGood%20question!%5D%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EProbably%20we%20should%20say%20a%20big%20thank%20you%20to%20you%20for%0Athis%20wonderful%20question.%20%20Right%20now%20we%20are%20going%20to%20receive%20a%0Alarge%20set%20of%20documents%2C%20microfilms%2C%20etc.%20from%20the%20Hoover%0AInstitute%20on%20Russian%20History.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EWe%20have%20preliminarily%20agreed%20to%20have%20the%20Smolensk%0AArchives%20(captured%20by%20Germans)%20returned%20to%20Russia.%20These%0Adocuments%20will%20become%20part%20of%20the%20school%20materials%20and%20texts%20for%0Aall%20Russian%20students%20of%20all%20ages.%20%20%20%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EBillington%3A%20%20I%20should%20add%20that%20when%20I%20accompanied%0APres.%20Reagan%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20he%20asked%20what%20would%20be%0Aappropriate%20to%20give%20to%20Russian%20Universities.%20I%20found%20out%20that%20no%0Astudents%20could%20get%20primary-source%20documents%2C%20so%20have%20given%20them%0Athe%20complete%20microfilm%20documents%20of%20Jefferson%2C%20Washington%20and%0ALincoln.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20university%20students%20had%20primary%0Adocuments%20to%20work%20on.%20I%20would%20hope%20that%20as%20our%20exchange%20would%0Adevelop%20we%20could%20share%20such%20things%20in%20schools%20and%20universities%0Aand%20archives.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ETipToe%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3E(Excellent!!!!!!!)%20ga%20%3A)%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EVGEngineer%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20position%20of%20the%20CIS%20concerning%0Athe%20Nuclear%20Non-Proliferation%20treaty%3F%20%20%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EThe%20position%20of%20the%20CIS%20on%20nuclear%20disarmament%20was%0Aagreed%20to%20by%20all%20the%20states%2C%20members%20of%20the%20CIS%20and%20the%20position%0Awas%20confirmed%20at%20the%20mtg%20of%20heads%20of%20state%20in%20Minsk%20and%0ATashkent--meetings%20held%20very%20recently.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EBCS%20Skip%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EI%20ya%20tozhe%20%3A)%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EBCS%20Skip%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3E(me%20too)%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ESovarc%2C%20one%20of%20our%20questions%20was%3A%20How%20were%20the%0Aarchives%20made%20available%20to%20the%20US%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EThe%20materials%20were%20provided%20to%20the%20Library%20of%0ACongress%2C%20the%20largest%20not%20only%20in%20the%20US%20but%20the%20largest%0Arepository%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20gov't%20of%20Russia%20believes%20it%20useful%0Ato%20familiarize%20Americans%20after%20a%20period%20of%20seventy%20years%20...and%0Athe%20L%20of%20C%20is%20the%20best%20way%20of%20getting%20this%20information%20to%20the%0AAmericans.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3A%20Which%20documents%20in%20the%20exhibit%20are%20likely%0Ato%20cause%20historians%20to%20re-evaluate%20key%20aspects%20of%20Soviet%20history%3F%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EI%20think%20that%20all%20of%20the%20documents%20will%20be%20cause%20for%0Aa%20reevaluation%20of%20Soviet%20history.%20Two%20hours%20ago%20there%20was%20a%0Aseminar%20held%20at%20the%20L%20of%20C%20in%20which%20some%20of%20the%20leading%20US%0Ahistorians%20were%20present%20and%20they%20share%20this%20point%20of%20view.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EBillington%3A%20%20I%20would%20add%20that%20the%20Lenin%20documents%0Athat%20show%20far%20more%20of%20the%20distinctive%20elements%20of%20totalitarianism%0Apresent%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Soviet%20experience%20are%20of%0Aparticular%20importance.%20Also%2C%20more%20recent%20documents%20showing%2C%20for%0Ainstance%2C%20that%20the%20preparations%20for%20Afghanistan%20were%20well%0Adeveloped%20earlier%20than%20previously%20thought.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20new%20contribution%20of%20all%20may%20be%20to%0Ashow%20the%20human%20factor%20at%20work%2C%20both%20the%20brilliance%20of%20repression%0Aand%20the%20strength%20and%20depth%20of%20opposition%20that%20was%20there%20all%0Aalong.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EUICLibrary%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3Ehow%20many%20CIS%20citizens%20will%20have%20access%20to%20the%0Aarchives%3F%20and%20how%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ERebeccaH%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EWill%20these%20documents%20be%20widely%20available%20inside%20the%0ACIS%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20we%20will%20provide%20access%2C%20we%20will%20make%0Aaccess%20to%20archives%20a%20lot%20easier...%20we%20are%20declassifying%20a%20large%0Anumber%20of%20these%20documents%2C%20and%20Russian%20specialists%20along%20with%20L%0Aof%20C%20are%20%20planning%20to%20publish%20series%20of%20books%20based%20on%20these%0Adocuments%20and%20these%20books%20will%20be%20available%20in%20the%20CIS%20and%20in%20the%0AUS.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ETeacherjh%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EHow%20might%20the%20Soviet%20people%20react%20%3Ddifferently%3D%20to%0Athese%20documents%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20American%20people%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%3A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EFor%20the%20American%20people%2C%20the%20documents%20are%20a%20matter%0Aof%20interest.%20For%20the%20peoples%20for%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20this%20is%20their%0Adestiny%2C%20this%20is%20their%20life.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3A%20Are%20there%20any%20documents%20that%20have%20serious%0Aimplications%20for%20Russian-US%20relations%3F%20Which%20ones%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EUS-Russian%20relations%20existed%20in%201917%20and%20are%0Aresuming%20in%201992.%20For%20the%20history%20of%20US%20Soviet%20relations%2C%20which%0Ahave%20already%20become%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%20there%20will%20be%20exposed%0Amany%2C%20many%20more%20new%20pages%20which%20will%20explain%20why%20the%20relations%0Abetween%20our%20two%20countries%20were%20the%20way%20they%20were.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3AWill%20the%20particular%20revelations%20about%20Lenin%0Afrom%20his%20personal%20memos%20accelerate%20his%20debunking%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EThere%20is%20a%20question%20in%20the%20question.%20%20History%20does%0Anot%20deal%20with%20debunking%20or%20glorifying.%20The%20purpose%20of%20history%20is%0Ato%20show%20how%20things%20really%20were.%20The%20real%20Lenin%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20a%0Alot%20closer%20to%20the%20real%20Stalin%20than%20people%20thought%20in%20the%20past.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3ADo%20you%20feel%20the%20exhibit's%20revelations%20will%0Abe%20a%20net%20plus%20or%20minus%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20increased%20US%20assistance%0Ato%20Russia%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EWe%2C%20the%20organizers%20of%20this%20exhibit%2C%20the%20Russian%0Agov't%20Committee%20on%20Archives%20and%20the%20L%20of%20C%20are%20convinced%20that%0Athis%20will%20help%20the%20cause%20of%20providing%20assistance%20because%20you%20help%0Athose%20whom%20you%20trust.%20This%20exhibit%20is%20precisely%20an%20indication%20of%0Athe%20trust%20that%20has%20developed%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Russia.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3ADo%20any%20documents%20in%20the%20archives%20pave%20the%0Away%20for%20increased%20exchange%20of%20more%20scientific%2Fartistic%20ideas%0Abetween%20the%20US-Russia%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EDr.%20Billington%3A%20%20No%20particular%20document%20paves%20such%20a%0Away.%20The%20very%20fact%20of%20sharing%20all%20of%20this%20material%20creates%20the%0Afirst%20and%20most%20fundamental%20precondition%20for%20true%20intellectual%20and%0Acultural%20exchange%2C%20which%20is%20the%20open%20and%20full%20sharing%20of%0Ainformation%20with%20other%20writers%20and%20creators.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EMoreover%2C%20by%20exposing%20the%20negative%20effects%20of%0Arepressing%20creative%20and%20spiritual%20life%2C%20you%20create%20a%20strengthened%0Abelief%20in%20the%20importance%20of%20those%20aspects%20of%20human%20life.%20So%2C%20this%0Ato%20me%20is%20a%20very%20hopeful%20swallow%20of%20a%20new%20spring%20of%20creative%0Ainteraction%20for%20America%20(speaking%20selfishly)%20with%20a%20great%20culture%0Awith%20which%20we%20have%20only%20partial%20contact%20these%20recent%20years.%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EJennifer05%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EQuestion%3A%20Does%20the%20exhibit%20have%20any%20revelations%0Aimpacting%20nationalities%20issues%20in%20Russia%2C%20particularly%20the%20ethnic%0Agroups%3F%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EProbably%2C%20these%20documents%20might%20be%20the%20information%0Aon%20the%20repression%20carried%20out%20against%20the%20Crimea%20and%20Tartars%2C%20the%0Aethnic%20Germans%2C%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20'30's%20and%20'40's.%20We%20are%0Aconvinced%20that%20the%20truth%20about%20these%20events%20has%20to%20be%20told%20as%20a%0Anecessary%20condition%20for%20normalizing%20the%20question%20of%20nationality.%20%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ESovarc%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3EDr.%20Pikhoia%20would%20like%20to%20know%20where%20the%20questioners%0Aare%20from.%20%20Please%20identify%20your%20city%20%26amp%3B%20state%20also.%20%20%20%0A%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ERich%20OO%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ENewport%20Beach%20California%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EGerryR52%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ESt.Paul%2C%20Minnesota...%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3EGazers%20%20%20%20%20%3A%20%3C%2Fdt%3E%3Cdd%3ELittle%20Falls%2C%20New%20Jersey%0A%3C%2Fdd%3E%3Cdt%3ETeach